## 📊 What Makes This Different from a CNN?

| Feature | DenseNet121 (Baseline) | This Model |
|---|---|---|
| Classification | ✅ Benign/Malignant | ✅ Benign/Malignant |
| Interpretability | ❌ Black box probability | ✅ Quantum ⟨Z⟩ values |
| Noise analysis | ❌ Not applicable | ✅ 4 noise types × 3 levels |
| Circuit comparison | ❌ Single architecture | ✅ 3 quantum architectures |
| Quantum advantage study | ❌ None | ✅ Core research question |
| NISQ readiness | ❌ Not applicable | ✅ Noise resilience proven |

